1
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh...</font>

2
00:00:20,860 --> 00:00:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

3
00:00:22,940 --> 00:00:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We said, anyone who would
 defy us must die.</font>

4
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no use! They've been 
completely brainwashed!</font>

5
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Outta the way!</font>

6
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You guys...</font>

7
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! What are you doing?!</font>

8
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help!</font>

9
00:01:41,980 --> 00:01:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you?</font>

10
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Electro-Wave Human, Tack'!</font>

11
00:02:01,650 --> 00:02:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Riderman!</font>

12
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mitsuba!</font>

13
00:02:09,580 --> 00:02:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like...</font>

14
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to do this.</font>

15
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

16
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it.</font>

17
00:04:24,710 --> 00:04:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've... finally been reunited, boys...</font>

18
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're leaving already?</font>

19
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still alive?</font>

20
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aniki, this is your chance!</font>

21
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of here!</font>

22
00:04:46,470 --> 00:04:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

23
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're all alive!</font>

24
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You risked your lives 
for a scumbag like me...</font>

25
00:05:11,170 --> 00:05:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

26
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't have asked 
for better brothers.</font>

27
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">.44 Magnum!</font>

28
00:06:10,790 --> 00:06:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao-san!</font>

29
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey.</font>

30
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm all done over here.</font>

31
00:06:17,690 --> 00:06:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you got your ass kicked.</font>

32
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

33
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'll be fine.</font>

34
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, we've got a monster to beat!</font>

35
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Aniki...</font>

36
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys...</font>

37
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you hit us, Aniki... 
that snapped us out of it.</font>

38
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm... I'm so...</font>

39
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're so sorry, Aniki! 
Please forgive us!</font>

40
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who should apologize.</font>

41
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're alive.</font>

42
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm sorry I didn't 
come back to help you.</font>

43
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aniki!</font>

44
00:07:32,090 --> 00:07:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here?</font>

45
00:07:34,010 --> 00:07:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The power of love freed them 
from their brainwashing!</font>

46
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao-san, we don't have 
a lot of time. We need to hurry!</font>

47
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

48
00:07:43,370 --> 00:07:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll show you the way!</font>

49
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

50
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking about it, if we're waiting for
 the signal at the climax of the show...</font>

51
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna have nothing 
to do until then!</font>

52
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a point.</font>

53
00:07:58,110 --> 00:08:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As important as the plan is, the sooner 
I get to fight Shocker, the better.</font>

54
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you, Mitsuba.</font>

55
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to avenge Grandpa and Grandma!</font>

56
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should've gone straight for the 
Bat Man instead of loafing around!</font>

57
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you fight me, then?</font>

58
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's you!</font>

59
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Spider Man!</font>

60
00:08:23,990 --> 00:08:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-You wretch!</font>

61
00:08:27,930 --> 00:08:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rider...</font>

62
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Transform! V3!</font>

63
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm joking.</font>

64
00:08:35,810 --> 00:08:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys really are entertaining.</font>

65
00:08:41,890 --> 00:08:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking forward to 
seeing how this turns out.</font>

66
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He vanished?</font>

67
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you guys can still transform, 
even without the brainwashing!</font>

68
00:09:10,170 --> 00:09:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like you, Aniki!</font>

69
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way!</font>

70
00:09:21,290 --> 00:09:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had a feeling you'd turn up.</font>

71
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raiko...</font>

72
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, please!</font>

73
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aniki?</font>

74
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Maybe you...</font>

75
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">aren't brainwashed anymore, either?</font>

76
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We spent all that time eating 
and training together, y'know?!</font>

77
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on!</font>

78
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll say it again.</font>

79
00:10:06,930 --> 00:10:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lov—</font>

80
00:10:10,570 --> 00:10:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aniki?!</font>

81
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Aniki!</font>

82
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even more traitors?</font>

83
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all going to die.</font>

84
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mitsuba-san.</font>

85
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave her to me.</font>

86
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on ahead.</font>

87
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood!</font>

88
00:10:43,730 --> 00:10:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

89
00:11:00,450 --> 00:11:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be fighting me.</font>

90
00:11:08,230 --> 00:11:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're the one 
who stayed behind.</font>

91
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pro wrestling is all about 
rubber matches, right?</font>

92
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, I'm going to beat you 
until you stop fighting back.</font>

93
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do you think you are?</font>

94
00:11:36,410 --> 00:11:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look stronger than before, too.</font>

95
00:11:40,890 --> 00:11:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That works for me!</font>

96
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Bat Man. It's time.</font>

97
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love's an amazing thing, huh?</font>

98
00:12:42,310 --> 00:12:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's stuff out there that I love. 
And people I love, too.</font>

99
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That fact alone is enough to make me 
feel like I'm on cloud nine!</font>

100
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raiko, you must really 
love pro wrestling.</font>

101
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on, how do you two know—</font>

102
00:13:05,650 --> 00:13:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't.</font>

103
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

104
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This old man taught me something.</font>

105
00:13:16,140 --> 00:13:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even a combatant can get stronger 
by training hard enough!</font>

106
00:13:23,310 --> 00:13:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raiko!</font>

107
00:13:27,090 --> 00:13:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I'm still a combatant...</font>

108
00:13:30,730 --> 00:13:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where is this pressure coming from?!</i></font>

109
00:13:33,730 --> 00:13:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can become stronger than a monster!</font>

110
00:13:48,190 --> 00:13:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why... can't I...</i></font>

111
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>move?!</i></font>

112
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raiko!</font>

113
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really <i>do</i> care about me!</font>

114
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so...</font>

115
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">damn happy!</font>

116
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, I love ya, Raiko!</font>

117
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did that finally shut you up?!</font>

118
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... feel I should ask...</font>

119
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even our enemy anymore?</font>

120
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am!</font>

121
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But all this "I love you" stuff...</font>

122
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're dead!</font>

123
00:15:21,330 --> 00:15:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rainmaker.</font>

124
00:15:36,970 --> 00:15:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My move...</font>

125
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is faster!</font>

126
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ultimate...</font>

127
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Electro-Wave Throw!</font>

128
00:16:11,970 --> 00:16:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unbelievable...</font>

129
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You countered Kazuchika Okada's 
Rainmaker with Naoya Ogawa's STO...</font>

130
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called an 
Ultimate Electro-Wave Throw.</font>

131
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lost again.</font>

132
00:16:56,930 --> 00:17:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To a normal human... 
not even a member of Shocker.</font>

133
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Her power...</font>

134
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the kind of thing 
half-baked feelings could produce.</font>

135
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the strength of her resolve... 
she was more determined than I was.</font>

136
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... want to be... stronger.</font>

137
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:43,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all ready?</font>

138
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

139
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

140
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

141
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All okay here!</font>

142
00:17:49,910 --> 00:17:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm in position too.</i></font>

143
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won?!</font>

144
00:17:54,090 --> 00:17:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Great job, Yuriko-san!</i></font>

145
00:17:58,220 --> 00:17:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

146
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone. Thank you so much 
for coming out today.</font>

147
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And before the show ends,</font>

148
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we have the best present ever to share 
with you, our beloved fans.</font>

149
00:18:59,390 --> 00:19:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now!</font>

150
00:19:11,390 --> 00:19:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fire?!</font>

151
00:19:13,990 --> 00:19:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Emergency. Emergency.</i></font>

152
00:19:17,250 --> 00:19:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There is a fire in the arena.</i></font>

153
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today's concert has been canceled.</i></font>

154
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All attendees, 
please follow staff instructions</i></font>

155
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and evacuate in an orderly fashion
 via the nearest emergency exit.</font>

156
00:19:30,590 --> 00:19:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I repeat...</font>

157
00:19:32,010 --> 00:19:34,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Emergency. Emergency.</i></font>

158
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Careful, everyone!</font>

159
00:19:35,450 --> 00:19:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't run, please!</font>

160
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Follow the individual in front of you 
to the exit without rushing!</font>

161
00:19:41,650 --> 00:19:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way!</font>

162
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let a single one of them escape!</font>

163
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

164
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:57,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so!</font>

165
00:20:06,610 --> 00:20:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raiko! To save you...</font>

166
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna take the boss's head!</font>

167
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tojima-san! Ichiyo! Now!</font>

168
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:25,700
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}LET'S DO THIS, SHOCKER!</b></font>

169
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do this, Shocker!</font>

170
00:20:31,210 --> 00:20:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

171
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">V3...</font>

172
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rider...</font>

173
00:20:42,930 --> 00:20:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Double Kick!</font>

174
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Bat Man!</font>

175
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you people?!</font>

176
00:20:56,910 --> 00:20:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">V3.</font>

177
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kamen Rider!</font>

178
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we've waited long enough!</font>

179
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your scheme ends here, Shocker!</font>

180
00:21:16,910 --> 00:21:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ruined everything...</font>

181
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you all die.</font>

182
00:21:43,810 --> 00:21:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive.</font>

183
00:21:46,810 --> 00:21:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But will you be able...</font>

184
00:21:50,950 --> 00:21:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to survive this time?</font>

185
00:23:24,970 --> 00:23:27,720
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}NEXT TIME</b></font>

